com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.security.model

Class CertificateEnrollmentListOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.common.listing.FilterOptions
      • com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.common.listing.ListOptions
        • com.arm.mbed.cloud.sdk.security.model.CertificateEnrollmentListOptions
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    @Preamble(description="Options to use when listing certificate enrollments.")
public class CertificateEnrollmentListOptions
extends ListOptions
    Options to use when listing certificate enrollments.

    Note:

    • Filters:

      The list can be filtered server-side on some of the fields of a certificate enrollment.

      The following filters are currently supported:

      Server-side filters
      Field Tag Filters
      not equal to equal to greater than less than like in not in
      enrollResult TAG_FILTER_BY_ENROLL_RESULT • •
      certificateName TAG_FILTER_BY_CERTIFICATE_NAME •
      updatedAt TAG_FILTER_BY_UPDATED_AT • •
      enrollStatus TAG_FILTER_BY_ENROLL_STATUS • •
      deviceId TAG_FILTER_BY_DEVICE_ID •
      createdAt TAG_FILTER_BY_CREATED_AT • •
